Hold on, now.
You're gonna be all right.

13
00:02:49,644 --> 00:02:52,579
Almost there.
Come on !

14
00:02:56,851 --> 00:02:59,319
- Hello, is this the emergency room?
- Yes, sir.

15
00:02:59,387 --> 00:03:01,981
- I'm bringing a child in.
- What is your emergency?

16
00:03:02,056 --> 00:03:04,524
I don't know!
I'm bringing a child in !

17
00:03:04,592 --> 00:03:06,992
