Come on, now, it's dinnertime.
Wash your hands.

413
00:33:22,675 --> 00:33:25,906
- I'm eating with Brady.
- No, come on, now.

414
00:33:26,846 --> 00:33:29,508
Michael, I'm sorry.
Brady invited him over for dinner.

415
00:33:29,582 --> 00:33:33,074
- I thought he'd asked you.
- Can I eat with Brady, Dad?

416
00:33:37,790 --> 00:33:41,248
Okay, it his dad
says it's all right.

417
00:33:41,327 --> 00:33:43,420
Is it all right, kids?

418
00:33:46,832 --> 00:33:49,323
I can fly!

419
00:34:06,419 --> 00:34:08,114
- Good afternoon, U Penn.
- Transcript office, please.

420
00:34:10,089 --> 00:34:13,581
-Transcripts.
