graduate work in our history department.

422
00:34:17,563 --> 00:34:20,862
I need to verify his
undergrad record with you guys.

423
00:34:21,934 --> 00:34:25,028
He's been out of school
for some time.

424
00:34:26,872 --> 00:34:28,806
The name's Oliver Lang.

425
00:34:29,976 --> 00:34:32,410
Are you telling me that you
took this out of his mailbox?

426
00:34:32,478 --> 00:34:35,003
- That is illegal.
- Tell me it you think this is strange.

427
00:34:35,081 --> 00:34:37,743
