434
00:34:56,102 --> 00:34:58,297
because they've got him mixed up
with somebody else.

435
00:34:58,371 --> 00:35:01,863
This U Penn Oliver
is the same age as Oliver.

436
00:35:01,941 --> 00:35:05,104
- Wait. As our Oliver?
- As our Oliver, yes.

437
00:35:05,177 --> 00:35:08,146
He graduated the same year, and...

438
00:35:08,214 --> 00:35:12,207
