460
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:17,476
God, you of all people.

461
00:36:19,118 --> 00:36:21,211
Are you teaching the Bill of Rights
this semester...

462
00:36:21,287 --> 00:36:23,881
or did that not make the program?

463
00:36:26,492 --> 00:36:29,586
I don't know what you're doing.
