585
00:48:07,359 --> 00:48:09,293
State of Kansas,
Department of Records.

586
00:48:09,361 --> 00:48:13,923
Yes, hi. Michael Jones.
I'm with the EEOC in Washington.

587
00:48:13,999 --> 00:48:19,027
