589
00:48:23,008 --> 00:48:24,942
Hold on, sir.

590
00:48:28,480 --> 00:48:31,040
Sir, I'm afraid I've got
nothing on any name change...

591
00:48:31,116 --> 00:48:33,482
for an Oliver Lang
of Carson, Kansas.

592
00:48:33,552 --> 00:48:35,645
Okay, just doin' my job.
Thank you.

593
00:48:35,720 --> 00:48:38,518
Sir? Our records indicate
Oliver Lang deceased...

594
00:48:38,590 --> 00:48:40,956
as of October 4, 1981.

595
00:48:41,026 --> 00:48:43,460
- October 4?
- Yes, sir.

596
00:48:50,435 --> 00:48:54,235
What does
the death certificate say?

597
00:48:55,006 --> 00:48:58,840
