622
00:50:24,829 --> 00:50:27,423
- This is important.
- My pension's important.

623
00:50:27,499 --> 00:50:30,730
Whit, I'm asking you to run a name.

624
00:50:30,802 --> 00:50:34,329
I'm not asking you to start surveillance
and break out the goddamn guns.

625
00:50:34,406 --> 00:50:38,467
Faraday, it you'd asked your wife to
do it, she'd tell you the same thing.

626
00:50:38,543 --> 00:50:40,841
Get you classified FBI information.

627
00:50:40,912 --> 00:50:43,506
She'd say,
"l love you, baby, but that...

628
00:50:43,582 --> 00:50:45,516
I cannot do."

629
00:50:47,085 --> 00:50:51,283
It you want to find out about somebody,
