630
00:50:51,356 --> 00:50:55,656
They're just not through me.
Come on. Use your imagination.

631
00:51:07,973 --> 00:51:10,703
Oh, hi, Daphne.
How you doin'?

632
00:51:12,043 --> 00:51:13,738
You doing okay?

633
00:51:17,482 --> 00:51:20,940
- Hi, Hannah.
- Mommy and Daddy aren't home.

634
00:51:21,019 --> 00:51:25,217
Oh, well, actually,
I don't need your mom and dad.

635
00:51:25,290 --> 00:51:29,386
You know what?
I locked myself out of my house.

636
00:51:29,461 --> 00:51:33,727
- I came home from work and realized--
- We can't let strangers in.

637
00:51:33,798 --> 00:51:36,631
Well, I'm not a stranger, right?

638
00:51:39,704 --> 00:51:43,037
See, what I need to do
is use your phone...

639
00:51:44,109 --> 00:51:48,978
to call up somebody to see if
they'll help me get in the house.

640
00:51:49,047 --> 00:51:52,016
Would that be all right...

641
00:51:52,851 --> 00:51:54,785
if I use your phone?

642
00:51:56,187 --> 00:51:59,748
- Kitchen.
- Good.

643
00:52:02,060 --> 00:52:04,824
I'm gonna use the phone
