692
00:57:28,386 --> 00:57:32,755
You know, American history.
Background on state militias.

693
00:57:32,824 --> 00:57:35,691
There's one in Kansas.

694
00:57:35,760 --> 00:57:38,627
Seems they got one everywhere.

695
00:57:38,696 --> 00:57:41,665
Jeez, I didn't know you taught
a course in terrorism.

696
00:57:41,733 --> 00:57:44,600
- That a pretty frightening subject.
- Yeah.

697
00:57:48,106 --> 00:57:52,543
- You got time for a drink?
- No, today's not good.

698
00:57:52,610 --> 00:57:54,771
Yeah, I hear ya.
I got a building contract...

699
00:57:54,846 --> 00:57:58,247
that's kickin' my butt
tryin' to put it together.

700
00:57:58,316 --> 00:58:00,181
Get back to work.

701
00:58:00,251 --> 00:58:03,516
Sorry to drop by.
Catch you back at the ranch.

702
00:58:03,588 --> 00:58:05,715
Good to see you.

703
00:58:08,960 --> 00:58:12,157
