that was cheating his father's farm.

709
00:58:30,214 --> 00:58:32,876
He served time
in a juvenile program.

710
00:58:34,218 --> 00:58:36,618
Pipe bomb as a kid.

711
00:58:36,687 --> 00:58:40,145
Why would you
go to these lengths...

712
00:58:40,224 --> 00:58:44,820
to hide that part of your history
if it wasn't an isolated event?

713
00:58:44,896 --> 00:58:47,023
